Answer the followingquestions for yourself and post your answers here. How did you develop your sense of ethics?   Is there aspecific individual in this organization or in theprofession that you look to as a model of ethicalbehavior?   What makes something ethical or unethical? How do you know if something is right or wrong?   How doyou make a moral choice ?  How do you decide thatsomething is ethical or unethical?   What would youadvise a new technical communicator to do if he/she wereasked to do something that he/she thought was unethical?  Is ethics a subject that you would like supervisors toaddress on the job? (If so, which topics would you liketo see covered?)   Is ethics a subject that you wouldlike teachers of technical communication to address intheir courses? (If so, which topics would you like tosee covered?)